des:
Listen to this story about bogeyman in your closet, technological progress, with omnipresent surveillance and cellphones has brought boogies to the forefront, in this story, listen if bogeyman adopts good energies, instead of preying on your fears. 
Will he be a magical Cheshire Cat, like in Wonderland? Listen on to find the good boogie of your boogieboard everywhere, plant a solar garden light for him, as he lives of the storage in it.
 At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
